                String.format("Entries size exceeded, only %d entries is accepted, message type is: %s",
                    size, getType()));
        }
    }

    @Override
    public boolean isCollection() {
        return true;
    }

    @Override
    public boolean isEmpty() {
        return size <= 0;
    }

    @Override
